# Quality gates on code updates (Maven)

- Run **`mvn verify`** on every backend code change when the project uses Maven.
- Fix Checkstyle, SpotBugs, and PMD violations before considering the change done.

From `be/`:

```bash
jenv shell 26
mvn verify
```
